Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.63,0:33:51.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们需要你做校音
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.46,0:33:53.24,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,因为除了你需要听 没人能听得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.24,0:33:55.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有的人也许不想从这基本的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.48,0:33:59.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我想要我写这首歌时的调子 听到的调子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.18,0:34:01.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,还有录音出来的调子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.49,0:34:02.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这就是我的全部要求
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.72,0:34:04.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是的 我们就是要这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.16,0:34:07.29,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,应该已经离你的要求不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.29,0:34:09.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你要听起来更高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.12,0:34:11.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.81,0:34:14.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,只有你可以决定 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.44,0:34:17.86,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,"听起来更高兴" 真有趣的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:21.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是你知道...你明白我的意思 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.48,0:34:22.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:24.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,再来一次 从最开始
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.99,0:34:46.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们来好好找找调子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.96,0:35:05.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,不 不 你们得再动情点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:08.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,- 这里有情感爆发 - 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:10.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你们没有爆发出来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.16,0:35:14.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有一瞬间 应该让感情爆发出来 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:18.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好吧 伙计们 有两个小节是从...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.50,0:35:21.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,至少一个小节
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.66,0:35:24.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好的 从刚才那儿再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.12,0:35:26.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,看看我们能找到什么相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.83,0:35:29.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.05,0:36:00.52,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Hey, pretty baby with the high heels on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.83,0:36:06.82,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,U give me fever like I'm never ever known!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.30,0:36:13.16,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I feel your fever from miles around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.21,0:36:18.57,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up in my car we'll paint the twon red.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.58,0:36:20.59,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Just kiss me baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:27.81,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,And tell me twice that you're the one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.81,0:36:33.54,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,The way you make me feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.18,0:36:39.14,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You real turn me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.79,0:36:45.74,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You knock me off of my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:50.39,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,My lonely days are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.15,0:37:02.63,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这地方我会给你手势 我给手势
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.63,0:37:04.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,不能随意来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.30,0:37:06.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伙计们 女伴舞得开始跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.68,0:37:09.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们配合还不默契 我会给手势的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:14.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你们得看着我做这个动作 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.40,0:37:38.96,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I never felt so in love before
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.77,0:37:43.44,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Just promise baby u'll love me forever more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.65,0:37:47.28,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm keeping you satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.02,0:37:50.36,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,'cause u're the one for me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.40,0:37:52.71,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,The way you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.34,0:37:56.85,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You real turn me yours
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.57,0:38:01.36,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You knock me off of my feet now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.90,0:39:20.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.92,0:39:25.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,像我们排练的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:27.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:28.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.60,0:39:34.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你想降八度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:37.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,可以了 不用降 那样太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.52,0:39:39.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,- 好的 我同意 - 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.88,0:39:42.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,- 只是后面... - 别管它了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.99,0:39:45.70,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,轻轻推上去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.92,0:39:49.06,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,MJ 我们装了鼓风机 就在舞台中央
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:50.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我没听清楚 再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:39:53.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,到时会有风扇 在舞台下面 为你设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.98,0:39:55.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.16,0:39:57.93,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,很好 注意 迈克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.33,0:41:08.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,再说一次 女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.64,0:41:10.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有请全世界最棒的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:12.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,杰克逊五兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.63,0:41:48.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,大家一起鼓掌 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.64,0:41:56.62,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,When I had you to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.66,0:41:58.61,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you around
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:02.93,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Out in a crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.16,0:42:05.08,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,But someone picked you from the bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.18,0:42:11.16,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Take a second look
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.23,0:42:16.03,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,To show you that I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.20,0:42:19.56,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Back in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.27,0:42:22.65,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Blind to let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.68,0:42:23.99,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Let you go, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.03,0:42:26.57,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,But now since I've seen you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.15,0:42:28.21,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I want you back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.25,0:42:29.14,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Yes I do now
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.18,0:42:30.23,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I want you back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.26,0:42:31.18,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Ooh ooh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.22,0:42:32.33,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I want you back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.36,0:42:33.30,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.34,0:42:34.39,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I want you back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.42,0:42:35.51,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Na na na na
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.54,0:42:36.60,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I want you back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.91,0:42:38.82,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伙计们 我必须得说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.23,0:42:40.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当我试图听耳机时
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.53,0:42:43.13,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就像有人把拳头打进我耳朵里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.25,0:42:45.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我很难听清
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.31,0:42:47.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我知道你们的初衷是好的 但实在是...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.30,0:42:51.01,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,试试调整一下我的耳机 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.29,0:42:53.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,带着爱的感觉去试试 L-O-V-E
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.49,0:42:54.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,迈克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.85,0:42:56.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,尽管不那么容易办到
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.21,0:42:58.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,迈克尔 重复一下 我听不到你 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.96,0:43:01.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你们升高音量时 我很难适应耳机
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.44,0:43:07.00,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,用你自己亲爱的耳朵试试
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.00,0:43:07.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.59,0:43:10.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就像有人把拳头...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.07,0:43:11.72,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,打进你耳朵里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.75,0:43:12.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.66,0:43:14.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我想听耳机但没法听
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.04,0:43:17.96,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我正在适应这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.97,0:43:21.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好的 迈克尔 在音量或者混音方面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:24.21,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,怎么调整耳机才能让你听得清
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.20,0:43:28.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,音量降低点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.98,0:43:30.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,请把音量降低点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.57,0:43:33.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,还有什么别的吗 迈克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.67,0:43:35.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,想多听到些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.45,0:43:37.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,多些声音或者多些...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.19,0:43:37.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.10,0:43:39.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好的 迈克尔 下首歌结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.56,0:43:42.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果依旧不符合你的要求 请跟我们说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.15,0:43:42.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.92,0:43:43.63,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.73,0:43:45.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你想从哪儿开始继续
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.92,0:43:48.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,- "停下来 你拯救的爱" - "停下来 你拯救的爱"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.32,0:44:02.95,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,When we played tag in grade school
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.98,0:44:04.42,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You wanted to be It.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.46,0:44:06.35,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,But chasing boys was just a fad
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.38,0:44:08.24,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You crossed your heart you'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.63,0:44:10.28,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,When we grew up you traded
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.32,0:44:11.93,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Your promise for my ring
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:14.15,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Now just like back to grade school
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.19,0:44:15.92,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You're doing the same old thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.96,0:44:19.00,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Stop! The love you save may be your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.03,0:44:20.69,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Darling, take it slow
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.73,0:44:23.32,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Or some day you'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.66,0:44:26.25,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You'd better stop the love you save may be your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.58,0:44:29.34,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Darling, look both ways before you cross me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.37,0:44:31.69,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You're headed for the danger zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.96,0:44:51.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你们
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.04,0:45:07.25,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You and I must make a pact
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.43,0:45:12.27,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,We must bring salvation back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.57,0:45:17.08,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Where there is love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.43,0:45:19.87,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.13,0:45:28.96,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll reach out my hand to you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:34.65,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I have faith in all you do
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.70,0:45:38.21,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Just call my name
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.77,0:45:41.95,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,And I'll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.38,0:45:50.44,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to comfort you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.47,0:45:53.71,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll build my world of dreams around you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.06,0:45:57.31,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I found you yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.34,0:46:01.00,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there with a love so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.04,0:46:03.04,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.00,0:46:07.17,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,You know I'll keep holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.52,0:46:18.79,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Baby yet you ever find someone new
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.44,0:46:25.17,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I know he better be good to you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.15,0:46:29.85,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,'Cause if he doesn't
