Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.72,0:46:50.53,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,Just call my name
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.20,0:46:55.45,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.30,0:47:04.39,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.87,0:47:09.72,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.39,0:47:20.15,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,There.
