Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.13,0:47:57.76,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I will be
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.12,0:48:01.97,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I will be
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.20,0:48:05.61,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I will be
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.89,0:48:12.46,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,I will be
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.75,0:48:26.83,BLC-50SP,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:30.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,- 灭灯 - 请保持后台清洁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.68,0:48:33.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,把特殊灯光去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.37,0:48:35.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,让侧影进来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.62,0:48:37.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我和那些伴舞们 我们和他一起排练
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.03,0:48:40.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一周两三次
